LIFECYCLE METHODS:
 Three methods:
 Mounting--- The component is ready to mount in the brownser dom. this phase covers the initialization from 
 1. constructor--for state declararyion
 2. getderivedstatesfromprops---rarely used lifecycle method
 3.render---each updation, dom will render
 4.componentdidmount---intial dom 

 updating--- 
 1. getderivedstatesfromprops
 2. shouldComponentUpdate 
 3. getSnapshotBeforeUpdate
 4. componentDidUpdate


